last_episode_to_air.name: Holiday Week Finals
last_episode_to_air.overview: It’s the Holiday Week Finals! With the help of their celebrity partners, the remaining players compete to become the first-ever Holiday Week Champion! And the winning team will take on the obstacle course to go for double the dollars.

name: Double Dare
overview: The all-new Double Dare with Liza Koshy has all the trivia, physical challenges, and obstacles for the messiest game show on TV!

episodes.name: The Juicy Pineapples vs. The Cavities
episodes.overview: It's twins vs. brothers in a series of messy challenges that include wet diapers and water shoes! While it's a tight matchup, it's the brains of one team that propels them into the final round.

episodes.name: The Mad Dogs vs. Line Drive 25
episodes.overview: Aim is the name of the game as best friends take on cousins in a series of squirting, throwing and stacking challenges. The teams are neck and neck, but when the buzzer rings only one moves onto the final round.

episodes.name: The Odd Couple vs. Gruesome Twosome
episodes.overview: Best friends take on step brothers in a series of edible challenges as they catapult giant pancakes and become human-sized bowls of fruit punch. But only one goes onto the bonus round!

episodes.name: Sisters on a Roll vs. Synergy Skaters
episodes.overview: Two teams compete in new, messy challenges of classic games, the water balloon and egg toss! However, in this high scoring game, one team pulls ahead and earns them a shot at the obstacle course.

episodes.name: A-Team vs. Team Peanut Butter
episodes.overview: Siblings take on best friends in a series of tossing games. And both teams realize they need to practice their aiming skills! Only one team moves on to the obstacle course.

episodes.name: Sync or Be Silly vs. Team Blonde
episodes.overview: It's buddies vs. besties in a series of wet, slippery, and balloon-popping challenges. While one team is determined to take on a number of physical challenges, it's the other team's brains that advance them to the final round.

episodes.name: EJ Grand Slammers vs. Santa Barbara Goldies
episodes.overview: Two teams of best friends compete in a series of balancing, throwing, and catching challenges. While one team struggles to learn that slow and steady wins the race, the other team's aim earns them a shot at the final round!

episodes.name: Team Toaster vs. Gummy Ninjas
episodes.overview: A messy mom and son compete against a dad and son team who aren't afraid of a little water! As they take on a bunch of edible challenges, only one wins enough points to move onto the bonus round.

episodes.name: The Twinadoes vs. Goofy Gamers
episodes.overview: Two teams compete in a series of messy games for the chance to win big! One team, is quick on their feet and earns a chance to run the final obstacle course.

episodes.name: Thunderstruck vs. Girl Power
episodes.overview: With the help of their teammates, Kira Kosarin takes on Olympian Lindsey Vonn. Though they both aim to win, only one team moves on to run the obstacle course!

episodes.name: Dominating Duo vs. Blast from the Past
episodes.overview: Former Double Dare teammates come back 30 years later for another matchup - this time with their kids! Although the game score is tight until the end, one team's physical endurance sends them into the final round.

episodes.name: The Showie Skaters vs. Home Run Homies
episodes.overview: It's skating sisters versus baseball playing brothers in a series of challenges that test their teamwork. One team puts their heads together to earn their spot in the final round!

episodes.name: Girls With a Goal vs. Team Nyris
episodes.overview: Two teams of friends face off in a series of buzzer beater challenges. One team's determination, brains, and teamwork in the physical challenges propel them to the final round.

episodes.name: Team Server vs. Team Spears
episodes.overview: It's a blast from the past when Josh Server and his niece take on Jamie Lynn Spears and her daughter at this "All That" reunion!

episodes.name: Little Mythical Fish vs. The Shortstacks
episodes.overview: In a competitive matchup, two brother-sister teams go head to head in a series of messy and high energy challenges. One team's energetic teamwork gets them to the final round.

episodes.name: Chatty Cheerleaders vs. Showtime Swag
episodes.overview: Featuring a special guest, two active sets of friends face off in a series of messy and wet challenges that put a new spin on household activities sending one team into the final round.

episodes.name: Who Runs the World vs. 2 Hype
episodes.overview: Best friends take on a brother-sister duo in a series of wet, silly, and epic challenges. One team's energy and teamwork propel them to the final round for an epic photo finish.

episodes.name: Blue Whales vs. The Flossinators
episodes.overview: A father and daughter take on a mother-son duo in a series of heated challenges and competitive trivia questions. With a major comeback at the end, one underdog team gets a shot at the obstacle course.

episodes.name: Board Bombs vs. Team Over Your Head
episodes.overview: It's athlete vs. athlete as Olympian Chloe Kim and her partner take on NBA player Andre Drummond and his teammate!

episodes.name: Comeback Kids vs. Red Hot Cocoa
episodes.overview: A couple of familiar faces come back for redemption after appearing on the show decades ago! It's a close game throughout, but only one team will get a second chance at the obstacle course.

episodes.name: Team Triple Threat vs. Wonder Triplet Power
episodes.overview: It's triplets versus triplets in an intense triple threat matchup! One team slays the trivia, earning them an epic shot at the final obstacle course.

episodes.name: Kickin' Cousins vs. Seeker Savages
episodes.overview: Cousins take on siblings in a series of messy challenges that test their teamwork! One teams special bond propels them into the final round where they have the chance to win big!

episodes.name: Run Girrrl vs. The Explorers
episodes.overview: An uncle and niece pair up against a mother-daughter duo in a competitive family battle. While one team struggles with the physical challenges, the other team sweeps the board and has an epic run on the obstacle course.

episodes.name: Team Rico vs. Team Raini
episodes.overview: It's a family reunion! Rico Rodriquez and his teammate take on Raini Rodriguez and her partner. It's a sibling rivalry until only one wins and moves forward to the obstacle course!

episodes.name: Team LaurDIY vs. Team Wassabi
episodes.overview: YouTubers, LaurDIY and Alex Wassabi team up with their fans for fun and messy head to head challenges! After a series of trivia questions and messy physical challenges, there's only room for one duo to move ahead to the final round!

episodes.name: Avocado Armpit vs. Bob 2
episodes.overview: It's friends vs. friends in an epic challenge! Each duo's trivia skills, strong physical expertise, and nifty teamwork leads to a neck and neck competition, launching only one team into the final round.

episodes.name: Football Fanatics vs. Bow-Tie Boys
episodes.overview: Sibling teams go head to head in a high-scoring game filled with running, launching, and aiming challenges. One team's brain power and physical endurance propels them to the top of leaderboard, earning them a chance at the obstacle course.

episodes.name: Double Scare
episodes.overview: In this Halloween special, friends take on twins in a series of classic challenges with a spooky twist! And only one team gets to compete in the ghostly final round.

episodes.name: Me, Lou and 2 vs. Beach Bums
episodes.overview: The whole family is involved! Families of four take on a series of super-sized challenges, but only one team can run the obstacle course together.

episodes.name: Fashionistos vs. Buzzer Beaters
episodes.overview: A team of clothes-obsessed besties takes on two competitive basketball players in a series of edible and messy challenges; one team proves that they can work together and moves on to the final round.

episodes.name: The Mighty Tweens vs. The Super Scouts
episodes.overview: Best friends take on a team of boy scouts in a series of tossing and racing challenges. One team's failed challenges cost them a shot at the final round.

episodes.name: Team Kel vs. Team Kenan
episodes.overview: Kel Mitchell & Kenan Thompson join their super fans for a competitive hour special. Although both teams struggle in the physical challenges, the ultimate test is the final obstacle course.

episodes.name: Hot Tamales vs. The Stylish Ones
episodes.overview: Kids team up with their moms in a series of messy challenges. Although it's a competitive match up throughout the game, one team's epic fail costs them a shot at the final obstacle course.

episodes.name: Double Dads vs. Cali Rally
episodes.overview: Two athletic families face off in a high scoring game filled with spills, spills, and more spills. A close game throughout, one team's physical endurance wins them a chance to take on the obstacle course.

episodes.name: Relentless Goats vs. Purple Pandas
episodes.overview: A father and son face off against a mother-daughter duo in a series of trivia questions and messy challenges. One team literally uses their heads to move onto the final round!

episodes.name: Dos Dames vs. Double Trouble
episodes.overview: It's double the fun with twins vs. twins in an epic battle of diapers, plungers, and even a cat-a-pult! But only one team of twins will get to take on the obstacle course!

episodes.name: The Singing Prancers vs. The Strikers
episodes.overview: Friends go head to head against cousins in a series of crazy time sensitive challenges. One team proves that teamwork truly makes the dream work and moves on to the final round!

episodes.name: Savage Cabbages vs. Evelyn Adrenaline
episodes.overview: Things get physical as two brothers take on the Evelyns in a series of back to back physical challenges. Although close at the start, one team's physical stamina sweeps the board.

episodes.name: Boardgame Bros vs. X-Treme Team
episodes.overview: A team of athletes takes on an extreme girl group! It's a game of boy versus girls until one team's brain power moves them forward to the final round!

episodes.name: Thunder & Lightning vs. The Slime Eaters
episodes.overview: In a multi-generational game of heated challenges, a girl and her grandma team up against a father-daughter duo. With high energy challenges and back to back trivia questions, it's a close game until the very end!

episodes.name: Kids' Choice Week Game 1
episodes.overview: Two 4-person teams compete in a series of brand new challenges for the chance to advance in the first-ever Kids' Choice Week Tournament! One team is quick on their feet and wins their chance to move on and play with their favorite KCA nominees.

episodes.name: Kids' Choice Week Game 2
episodes.overview: KCA nominees Emma Chamberlain and Guava Juice team up with their fans for messy head to head challenges! Though both teams aim to win, only one pair can move on to the all-new obstacle course and tournament Finals.

episodes.name: Kids' Choice Week Game 3
episodes.overview: The remaining KCA Week Finalists are set when nominees Pete Wentz and Joel Courtney face off with their teammates in a series of trivia questions and physical challenges for the chance to take on the obstacle course!

episodes.name: Kids' Choice Week Finals
episodes.overview: It’s the Kids’ Choice Week Finals! With their celeb partners, the remaining players compete to be the first-ever Kids' Choice Week Champion! The winning team will run the obstacle course for the biggest cash prize in Double Dare history.

episodes.name: WWE Superstars Week Game 1
episodes.overview: Two 4-person teams compete in a series of challenges for the chance to advance in the first-ever WWE Superstars Week Tournament! One team maneuvers their way onto the obstacle course and into the next game to play with their favorite WWE Superstars.

episodes.name: WWE Superstars Week Game 2
episodes.overview: WWE Superstars Week continues this time with Superstars Nikki and Brie Bella and their returning teammates! It’s a close call, but when the bell rings only one duo moves onto the legendary obstacle course and tournament finals.

episodes.name: WWE Superstars Week Game 3
episodes.overview: WWE Superstars, The New Day, team up with their fans to go head to head! But it’s one pair’s determination, brains, and teamwork that propels them onto the obstacle course and into the finals.

episodes.name: WWE Superstars Week Finals
episodes.overview: It’s the WWE Superstars Week Finals! With their Superstars, the remaining kids compete to become the first-ever WWE Superstars Week Champion! The winning team has a final smackdown with the obstacle course for a chance to win double the dollars.

episodes.name: SpongeBob Week Game 1
episodes.overview: Two 4-person teams compete in a series of challenges for the chance to advance in the first-ever SpongeBob Week Tournament! Only one squad will swim their way onto the obstacle course and into the next games to play with their favorite celebrities.

episodes.name: SpongeBob Week Game 2
episodes.overview: SpongeBob week continues with Drake Bell and Guava Juice and their returning teammates! It’s a competitive game throughout, but only one duo will earn their spot in the finals and get a chance at the obstacle course.

episodes.name: SpongeBob Week Game 3
episodes.overview: Jason Sudeikis and Tiffany Haddish team up with their fans to go fin to fin in the ultimate Bikini Bottom battle! One team’s energetic teamwork gets them onto the obstacle course and into the tournament finals.

episodes.name: SpongeBob Week Finals
episodes.overview: It’s the SpongeBob Week Finals! With the help of their celebrity partners, the remaining kids compete to become the first-ever SpongeBob Week Champion! And the winning team will take on the obstacle course to go for double the dollars.

episodes.name: Halloween Week Game 1
episodes.overview: Two 4-person teams compete in a series of ghostly trivia and spooky challenges for the chance to advance in the Halloween Week Tournament! But only one team moves on to play with their favorite celebrities.

episodes.name: Halloween Week Game 2
episodes.overview: Celebrities Baby Ariel and Anna Camp team up with their fans for tricky trivia and messy Halloween challenges! One team proves that teamwork truly makes the dream work and moves on to the obstacle course and lands a spot in the tournament finals!

episodes.name: Halloween Week Game 3
episodes.overview: The remaining Halloween Week finalists are set when professional athletes Martellus Bennett and Nick Young face off with their teammates in a series of ghastly questions and chilling challenges. One team dominates and gets to run the obstacle course!

episodes.name: Halloween Week Finals
episodes.overview: It’s the Halloween Week Finals! With the help of their celebrity partners, the remaining players compete to become the Halloween Week Champion! And the winning team will take on the obstacle course to go for double the dollars.

episodes.name: Holiday Week Game 1
episodes.overview: Two 4-person teams compete in a series of brand new challenges for the chance to advance in the first-ever Holiday Week Tournament! Two families go head to head, but only one moves on to play with their favorite holiday lovin’ celebrities.

episodes.name: Holiday Week Game 2
episodes.overview: Two returning kids team up with their favorite celebrities, Ally Brooke and Duff Goldman! One team pulls ahead and earns themselves a shot at the obstacle course and a spot in the Finals!

episodes.name: Holiday Week Game 3
episodes.overview: Tiffany Haddish and Shaun White team up with their fans for a festive face off! As they take on a series of messy challenges, only one wins enough points to move onto the obstacle course and tournament Finals.

episodes.name: Holiday Week Finals
episodes.overview: It’s the Holiday Week Finals! With the help of their celebrity partners, the remaining players compete to become the first-ever Holiday Week Champion! And the winning team will take on the obstacle course to go for double the dollars.
